{"doc":{"body":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"u1944b30a\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Hooks 的依赖数组是 React 用来判断 Effect、Memo 或 Callback 是否需要重新执行的核心机制。其原理可以概括为：</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">基于调用顺序和浅比较，决定是否跳过更新</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">。下面从设计目的、底层存储、比较逻辑以及注意事项四个方面详细说明。</span></p><hr id=\"W4bWp\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"DDsnA\"><span class=\"ne-text\">1. 依赖数组的设计目的</span></h2><p id=\"uc86e36ef\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">依赖数组让开发者能够声明式地指定 Hooks 所依赖的外部值（如 props、state）。当组件重新渲染时，React 会比较依赖项的新旧值：</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ufcd6e49b\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果所有依赖项都未变化，则跳过本次 Effect 的执行（或返回缓存的 Memo/Callback 值）。</span></li><li id=\"u1bab1189\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果有任何依赖项发生变化，则执行 Effect（或重新计算 Memo/Callback）。</span></li></ul><p id=\"ue3248bd5\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">这避免了不必要的计算和副作用，是 React 性能优化的重要手段。</span></p><hr id=\"YymDj\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"I4f21\"><span class=\"ne-text\">2. 底层存储：Fiber 中的 Hooks 链表</span></h2><p id=\"uf6a8a86f\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">每个函数组件对应一个 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">Fiber 节点</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，该节点上的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">memoizedState</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 属性指向一个</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">链表</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，链表中的每个节点对应组件中使用的一个 Hook（如 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useState</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">、</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useEffect</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">、</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useCallback</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 等）。</span></p><p id=\"ua238f010\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">对于 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useEffect</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，其 Hook 节点内部会存储：</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ufbe61cae\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">create</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：effect 函数。</span></li><li id=\"u89bd33b1\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">destroy</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：上一次执行返回的清理函数。</span></li><li id=\"ua845a2c2\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">deps</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：上一次渲染时传入的依赖数组。</span></li><li id=\"u88be6786\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">next</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：指向下一个 Hook 的指针。</span></li></ul><p id=\"uf3eacb3b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">当组件更新时，React 会按</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">绝对相同的顺序</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">遍历这个链表，依次取出每个 Hook 的上一次依赖数组，与本次传入的新依赖数组进行比较。</span></p><hr id=\"CR80o\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"BmtMh\"><span class=\"ne-text\">3. 比较逻辑：浅比较（</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">）</span></h2><p id=\"u9f9282b4\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">React 使用 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 对依赖项进行逐个比较，其行为与 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">===</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 基本一致，但有两个特例：</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u49718422\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">NaN === NaN</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">false</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，而 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is(NaN, NaN)</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">true</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">。</span></li><li id=\"ufced60f1\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">+0 === -0</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">true</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，而 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is(+0, -0)</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">false</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">。</span></li></ul><h3 id=\"BVDEZ\"><span class=\"ne-text\">比较过程</span></h3><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"mbDns\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>// 伪代码示意\nif (oldDeps === null) {\n  // 首次渲染，一定执行\n  return true;\n}\nfor (let i = 0; i &lt; oldDeps.length; i++) {\n  if (!Object.is(newDeps[i], oldDeps[i])) {\n    return true; // 有变化，需要执行\n  }\n}\nreturn false; // 无变化，跳过</code></pre><p id=\"ub8f0e0f5\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">注意：依赖数组的</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">长度必须保持不变</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，否则 React 会抛出警告（因为长度变化意味着调用顺序可能被破坏）。</span></p><hr id=\"izC6P\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"N2WUy\"><span class=\"ne-text\">4. 特殊情况的处理</span></h2><h3 id=\"OM8Fr\"><span class=\"ne-text\">4.1 空依赖数组 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">[]</span></code></h3><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u475ada11\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">首次渲染时会记录依赖数组 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">[]</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">。</span></li><li id=\"u014970c0\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">后续更新时，由于依赖项个数为 0，比较结果永远为“无变化”，因此 Effect 只执行一次（类似 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">componentDidMount</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">），清理函数在组件卸载时执行（类似 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">componentWillUnmount</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">）。</span></li></ul><h3 id=\"hXvGx\"><span class=\"ne-text\">4.2 不传第二个参数</span></h3><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u6f39d7a9\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">相当于没有依赖数组，React 会在每次渲染后都执行 Effect（先清理再执行），不进行任何跳过判断。</span></li></ul><h3 id=\"vgN4W\"><span class=\"ne-text\">4.3 依赖项为引用类型</span></h3><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u7d30b203\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果依赖项是对象、数组或函数，React 比较的是它们的</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">引用地址</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，而不是内容。例如：</span></li></ul><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"KVEXG\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>const [user, setUser] = useState({ name: 'Alice' });\nuseEffect(() =&gt; {}, [user]); // 即使 user 内容不变，但若 setUser({ name: 'Alice' }) 传入新对象，引用变化，Effect 会执行。</code></pre><p id=\"ue26b650e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">为避免不必要的执行，通常需要稳定依赖（如使用 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useMemo</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">/</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useCallback</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 或基于值的比较）。</span></p><hr id=\"iH7Rh\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"XLzd0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">5. 为什么必须保证调用顺序不变？</span></h2><p id=\"uf6061061\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">因为 React 完全依赖</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">调用顺序</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">来匹配每个 Hook 的依赖数组。如果 Hooks 被放在条件语句中，渲染顺序可能变化，导致链表索引错乱，React 会把前一个 Hook 的依赖数组误认为是后一个 Hook 的，从而引发 bug。这也是 Hooks 规则中强调“只在最顶层调用 Hooks”的根本原因。</span></p><hr id=\"ZLwpf\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"FFMZV\"><span class=\"ne-text\">6. 总结</span></h2><p id=\"u31b2bb8c\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Hooks 依赖数组的原理可以归结为：</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">React 在 Fiber 节点上按调用顺序存储每个 Hook 的上一次依赖数组，更新时使用 </span></strong><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code><strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 逐个比较新旧依赖项，从而决定是否跳过本次更新。</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 这一机制既保证了性能，又要求开发者遵循 Hooks 的调用规则。</span></p></div>","body_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"paragraphSpacing\" content=\"relax\" /><p data-lake-id=\"u1944b30a\" id=\"u1944b30a\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufaab4825\" id=\"ufaab4825\">Hooks 的依赖数组是 React 用来判断 Effect、Memo 或 Callback 是否需要重新执行的核心机制。其原理可以概括为：</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua63e6f7a\" id=\"ua63e6f7a\">基于调用顺序和浅比较，决定是否跳过更新</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u436d06ba\" id=\"u436d06ba\">。下面从设计目的、底层存储、比较逻辑以及注意事项四个方面详细说明。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22W4bWp%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"DDsnA\" id=\"DDsnA\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5249c0ce\" id=\"u5249c0ce\">1. 依赖数组的设计目的</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"uc86e36ef\" id=\"uc86e36ef\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0bfbed4c\" id=\"u0bfbed4c\">依赖数组让开发者能够声明式地指定 Hooks 所依赖的外部值（如 props、state）。当组件重新渲染时，React 会比较依赖项的新旧值：</span></p><ul list=\"u1edc8ef2\"><li fid=\"u556711a6\" data-lake-id=\"ufcd6e49b\" id=\"ufcd6e49b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6053b1e4\" id=\"u6053b1e4\">如果所有依赖项都未变化，则跳过本次 Effect 的执行（或返回缓存的 Memo/Callback 值）。</span></li><li fid=\"u556711a6\" data-lake-id=\"u1bab1189\" id=\"u1bab1189\"><span data-lake-id=\"u51f08543\" id=\"u51f08543\">如果有任何依赖项发生变化，则执行 Effect（或重新计算 Memo/Callback）。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"ue3248bd5\" id=\"ue3248bd5\"><span data-lake-id=\"ucf880c98\" id=\"ucf880c98\">这避免了不必要的计算和副作用，是 React 性能优化的重要手段。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22YymDj%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"I4f21\" id=\"I4f21\"><span data-lake-id=\"ueea03945\" id=\"ueea03945\">2. 底层存储：Fiber 中的 Hooks 链表</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"uf6a8a86f\" id=\"uf6a8a86f\"><span data-lake-id=\"uaad4c04f\" id=\"uaad4c04f\">每个函数组件对应一个 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ucd5f272f\" id=\"ucd5f272f\">Fiber 节点</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5032d4af\" id=\"u5032d4af\">，该节点上的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u9a5eabef\" id=\"u9a5eabef\"><span data-lake-id=\"uee3402b0\" id=\"uee3402b0\">memoizedState</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u82640cde\" id=\"u82640cde\"> 属性指向一个</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue2ccd91a\" id=\"ue2ccd91a\">链表</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc60a3d35\" id=\"uc60a3d35\">，链表中的每个节点对应组件中使用的一个 Hook（如 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ue23f227f\" id=\"ue23f227f\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub7c1b786\" id=\"ub7c1b786\">useState</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u36c29938\" id=\"u36c29938\">、</span><code data-lake-id=\"u09e2fa49\" id=\"u09e2fa49\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6a6f88df\" id=\"u6a6f88df\">useEffect</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u49845f6c\" id=\"u49845f6c\">、</span><code data-lake-id=\"u3238fe44\" id=\"u3238fe44\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2fa56089\" id=\"u2fa56089\">useCallback</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ua8dfdf31\" id=\"ua8dfdf31\"> 等）。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ua238f010\" id=\"ua238f010\"><span data-lake-id=\"u81c5f88c\" id=\"u81c5f88c\">对于 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ubfb03ea4\" id=\"ubfb03ea4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u38d5e6bb\" id=\"u38d5e6bb\">useEffect</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uf1653209\" id=\"uf1653209\">，其 Hook 节点内部会存储：</span></p><ul list=\"uf4cc3484\"><li fid=\"ue48b4381\" data-lake-id=\"ufbe61cae\" id=\"ufbe61cae\"><code data-lake-id=\"ua06d4d07\" id=\"ua06d4d07\"><span data-lake-id=\"uab65ff65\" id=\"uab65ff65\">create</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u05965911\" id=\"u05965911\">：effect 函数。</span></li><li fid=\"ue48b4381\" data-lake-id=\"u89bd33b1\" id=\"u89bd33b1\"><code data-lake-id=\"ub90a5449\" id=\"ub90a5449\"><span data-lake-id=\"uabdcb845\" id=\"uabdcb845\">destroy</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ufbf98311\" id=\"ufbf98311\">：上一次执行返回的清理函数。</span></li><li fid=\"ue48b4381\" data-lake-id=\"ua845a2c2\" id=\"ua845a2c2\"><code data-lake-id=\"u3a95f0e8\" id=\"u3a95f0e8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u102f4f4f\" id=\"u102f4f4f\">deps</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ud18e24cc\" id=\"ud18e24cc\">：上一次渲染时传入的依赖数组。</span></li><li fid=\"ue48b4381\" data-lake-id=\"u88be6786\" id=\"u88be6786\"><code data-lake-id=\"u43d93679\" id=\"u43d93679\"><span data-lake-id=\"u58a93fda\" id=\"u58a93fda\">next</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u94707b9f\" id=\"u94707b9f\">：指向下一个 Hook 的指针。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"uf3eacb3b\" id=\"uf3eacb3b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8c117bc7\" id=\"u8c117bc7\">当组件更新时，React 会按</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uec04c290\" id=\"uec04c290\">绝对相同的顺序</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u98b43201\" id=\"u98b43201\">遍历这个链表，依次取出每个 Hook 的上一次依赖数组，与本次传入的新依赖数组进行比较。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22CR80o%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"BmtMh\" id=\"BmtMh\"><span data-lake-id=\"u73e1b1f2\" id=\"u73e1b1f2\">3. 比较逻辑：浅比较（</span><code data-lake-id=\"ua1a5d29c\" id=\"ua1a5d29c\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7a2de18a\" id=\"u7a2de18a\">Object.is</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u4fa15a88\" id=\"u4fa15a88\">）</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u9f9282b4\" id=\"u9f9282b4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u94077698\" id=\"u94077698\">React 使用 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u9f42b93b\" id=\"u9f42b93b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4fa5b147\" id=\"u4fa5b147\">Object.is</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ud58e6804\" id=\"ud58e6804\"> 对依赖项进行逐个比较，其行为与 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u4a5cc75d\" id=\"u4a5cc75d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u069c2360\" id=\"u069c2360\">===</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"udc94a092\" id=\"udc94a092\"> 基本一致，但有两个特例：</span></p><ul list=\"u212b77b1\"><li fid=\"ua5d878cf\" data-lake-id=\"u49718422\" id=\"u49718422\"><code data-lake-id=\"uec53e75b\" id=\"uec53e75b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4bab5282\" id=\"u4bab5282\">NaN === NaN</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u4ce85a61\" id=\"u4ce85a61\"> 为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u36370738\" id=\"u36370738\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9ed98771\" id=\"u9ed98771\">false</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u05ce7183\" id=\"u05ce7183\">，而 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u26e658ba\" id=\"u26e658ba\"><span data-lake-id=\"u97e29458\" id=\"u97e29458\">Object.is(NaN, NaN)</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ua1521cda\" id=\"ua1521cda\"> 为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u49089610\" id=\"u49089610\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6c485cce\" id=\"u6c485cce\">true</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ub1414e2b\" id=\"ub1414e2b\">。</span></li><li fid=\"ua5d878cf\" data-lake-id=\"ufced60f1\" id=\"ufced60f1\"><code data-lake-id=\"u4e175f7e\" id=\"u4e175f7e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u04334cb7\" id=\"u04334cb7\">+0 === -0</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uf22ec731\" id=\"uf22ec731\"> 为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ufdaa8919\" id=\"ufdaa8919\"><span data-lake-id=\"ueec2e000\" id=\"ueec2e000\">true</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u9af737fc\" id=\"u9af737fc\">，而 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ua8c3bc98\" id=\"ua8c3bc98\"><span data-lake-id=\"uead8f67c\" id=\"uead8f67c\">Object.is(+0, -0)</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u6ec08727\" id=\"u6ec08727\"> 为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uc9990e4d\" id=\"uc9990e4d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u82445473\" id=\"u82445473\">false</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u4e3c0d10\" id=\"u4e3c0d10\">。</span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id=\"BVDEZ\" id=\"BVDEZ\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua07e1107\" id=\"ua07e1107\">比较过程</span></h3><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%2F%2F%20%E4%BC%AA%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E7%A4%BA%E6%84%8F%5Cnif%20(oldDeps%20%3D%3D%3D%20null)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%2F%2F%20%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E6%B8%B2%E6%9F%93%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%5Cn%20%20return%20true%3B%5Cn%7D%5Cnfor%20(let%20i%20%3D%200%3B%20i%20%3C%20oldDeps.length%3B%20i%2B%2B)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20if%20(!Object.is(newDeps%5Bi%5D%2C%20oldDeps%5Bi%5D))%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20true%3B%20%2F%2F%20%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%8C%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%5Cn%20%20%7D%5Cn%7D%5Cnreturn%20false%3B%20%2F%2F%20%E6%97%A0%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%8C%E8%B7%B3%E8%BF%87%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22mbDns%22%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"ub8f0e0f5\" id=\"ub8f0e0f5\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5b260b57\" id=\"u5b260b57\">注意：依赖数组的</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua532ddaa\" id=\"ua532ddaa\">长度必须保持不变</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5aa17101\" id=\"u5aa17101\">，否则 React 会抛出警告（因为长度变化意味着调用顺序可能被破坏）。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22izC6P%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"N2WUy\" id=\"N2WUy\"><span data-lake-id=\"u81c2c8c9\" id=\"u81c2c8c9\">4. 特殊情况的处理</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id=\"OM8Fr\" id=\"OM8Fr\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4bdff763\" id=\"u4bdff763\">4.1 空依赖数组 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u0d2a2372\" id=\"u0d2a2372\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8df72e76\" id=\"u8df72e76\">[]</span></code></h3><ul list=\"u0b89e119\"><li fid=\"u44f1140a\" data-lake-id=\"u475ada11\" id=\"u475ada11\"><span data-lake-id=\"u70c5f60a\" id=\"u70c5f60a\">首次渲染时会记录依赖数组 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u52a246d6\" id=\"u52a246d6\"><span data-lake-id=\"u86b788a3\" id=\"u86b788a3\">[]</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ub8d58b0b\" id=\"ub8d58b0b\">。</span></li><li fid=\"u44f1140a\" data-lake-id=\"u014970c0\" id=\"u014970c0\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3f031eea\" id=\"u3f031eea\">后续更新时，由于依赖项个数为 0，比较结果永远为“无变化”，因此 Effect 只执行一次（类似 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u60f73b39\" id=\"u60f73b39\"><span data-lake-id=\"u15144966\" id=\"u15144966\">componentDidMount</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uff798836\" id=\"uff798836\">），清理函数在组件卸载时执行（类似 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u142eedfc\" id=\"u142eedfc\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue3aec64b\" id=\"ue3aec64b\">componentWillUnmount</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u788e10fb\" id=\"u788e10fb\">）。</span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id=\"hXvGx\" id=\"hXvGx\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1761fb70\" id=\"u1761fb70\">4.2 不传第二个参数</span></h3><ul list=\"ufb82370b\"><li fid=\"ue07d3b77\" data-lake-id=\"u6f39d7a9\" id=\"u6f39d7a9\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf9a7d0ef\" id=\"uf9a7d0ef\">相当于没有依赖数组，React 会在每次渲染后都执行 Effect（先清理再执行），不进行任何跳过判断。</span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id=\"vgN4W\" id=\"vgN4W\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5b3ac037\" id=\"u5b3ac037\">4.3 依赖项为引用类型</span></h3><ul list=\"uaaaa7a89\"><li fid=\"u17ce8fc9\" data-lake-id=\"u7d30b203\" id=\"u7d30b203\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3c202496\" id=\"u3c202496\">如果依赖项是对象、数组或函数，React 比较的是它们的</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u493fa7e2\" id=\"u493fa7e2\">引用地址</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua23fdab2\" id=\"ua23fdab2\">，而不是内容。例如：</span></li></ul><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22const%20%5Buser%2C%20setUser%5D%20%3D%20useState(%7B%20name%3A%20'Alice'%20%7D)%3B%5CnuseEffect(()%20%3D%3E%20%7B%7D%2C%20%5Buser%5D)%3B%20%2F%2F%20%E5%8D%B3%E4%BD%BF%20user%20%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%98%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E8%8B%A5%20setUser(%7B%20name%3A%20'Alice'%20%7D)%20%E4%BC%A0%E5%85%A5%E6%96%B0%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%95%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%8CEffect%20%E4%BC%9A%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%82%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22KVEXG%22%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"ue26b650e\" id=\"ue26b650e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u15f34c80\" id=\"u15f34c80\">为避免不必要的执行，通常需要稳定依赖（如使用 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u7bc11d22\" id=\"u7bc11d22\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8d112582\" id=\"u8d112582\">useMemo</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u82729571\" id=\"u82729571\">/</span><code data-lake-id=\"u291db80b\" id=\"u291db80b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u88e3bb11\" id=\"u88e3bb11\">useCallback</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u951d4020\" id=\"u951d4020\"> 或基于值的比较）。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22iH7Rh%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"XLzd0\" id=\"XLzd0\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud7c1f25c\" id=\"ud7c1f25c\">5. 为什么必须保证调用顺序不变？</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"uf6061061\" id=\"uf6061061\"><span data-lake-id=\"u955a842f\" id=\"u955a842f\">因为 React 完全依赖</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2f2416e3\" id=\"u2f2416e3\">调用顺序</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5c4dec04\" id=\"u5c4dec04\">来匹配每个 Hook 的依赖数组。如果 Hooks 被放在条件语句中，渲染顺序可能变化，导致链表索引错乱，React 会把前一个 Hook 的依赖数组误认为是后一个 Hook 的，从而引发 bug。这也是 Hooks 规则中强调“只在最顶层调用 Hooks”的根本原因。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22ZLwpf%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"FFMZV\" id=\"FFMZV\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3d67ff26\" id=\"u3d67ff26\">6. 总结</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u31b2bb8c\" id=\"u31b2bb8c\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2e6250bd\" id=\"u2e6250bd\">Hooks 依赖数组的原理可以归结为：</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5ee4d6d4\" id=\"u5ee4d6d4\">React 在 Fiber 节点上按调用顺序存储每个 Hook 的上一次依赖数组，更新时使用 </span></strong><code data-lake-id=\"u8d5ac40d\" id=\"u8d5ac40d\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf979c216\" id=\"uf979c216\">Object.is</span></code><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5c2948c7\" id=\"u5c2948c7\"> 逐个比较新旧依赖项，从而决定是否跳过本次更新。</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uddcb8fd2\" id=\"uddcb8fd2\"> 这一机制既保证了性能，又要求开发者遵循 Hooks 的调用规则。</span></p>","body_draft":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"u1944b30a\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Hooks 的依赖数组是 React 用来判断 Effect、Memo 或 Callback 是否需要重新执行的核心机制。其原理可以概括为：</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">基于调用顺序和浅比较，决定是否跳过更新</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">。下面从设计目的、底层存储、比较逻辑以及注意事项四个方面详细说明。</span></p><hr id=\"W4bWp\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"DDsnA\"><span class=\"ne-text\">1. 依赖数组的设计目的</span></h2><p id=\"uc86e36ef\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">依赖数组让开发者能够声明式地指定 Hooks 所依赖的外部值（如 props、state）。当组件重新渲染时，React 会比较依赖项的新旧值：</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ufcd6e49b\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果所有依赖项都未变化，则跳过本次 Effect 的执行（或返回缓存的 Memo/Callback 值）。</span></li><li id=\"u1bab1189\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果有任何依赖项发生变化，则执行 Effect（或重新计算 Memo/Callback）。</span></li></ul><p id=\"ue3248bd5\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">这避免了不必要的计算和副作用，是 React 性能优化的重要手段。</span></p><hr id=\"YymDj\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"I4f21\"><span class=\"ne-text\">2. 底层存储：Fiber 中的 Hooks 链表</span></h2><p id=\"uf6a8a86f\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">每个函数组件对应一个 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">Fiber 节点</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，该节点上的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">memoizedState</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 属性指向一个</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">链表</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，链表中的每个节点对应组件中使用的一个 Hook（如 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useState</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">、</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useEffect</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">、</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useCallback</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 等）。</span></p><p id=\"ua238f010\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">对于 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useEffect</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，其 Hook 节点内部会存储：</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ufbe61cae\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">create</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：effect 函数。</span></li><li id=\"u89bd33b1\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">destroy</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：上一次执行返回的清理函数。</span></li><li id=\"ua845a2c2\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">deps</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：上一次渲染时传入的依赖数组。</span></li><li id=\"u88be6786\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">next</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：指向下一个 Hook 的指针。</span></li></ul><p id=\"uf3eacb3b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">当组件更新时，React 会按</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">绝对相同的顺序</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">遍历这个链表，依次取出每个 Hook 的上一次依赖数组，与本次传入的新依赖数组进行比较。</span></p><hr id=\"CR80o\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"BmtMh\"><span class=\"ne-text\">3. 比较逻辑：浅比较（</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">）</span></h2><p id=\"u9f9282b4\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">React 使用 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 对依赖项进行逐个比较，其行为与 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">===</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 基本一致，但有两个特例：</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u49718422\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">NaN === NaN</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">false</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，而 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is(NaN, NaN)</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">true</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">。</span></li><li id=\"ufced60f1\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">+0 === -0</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">true</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，而 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is(+0, -0)</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">false</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">。</span></li></ul><h3 id=\"BVDEZ\"><span class=\"ne-text\">比较过程</span></h3><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"mbDns\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>// 伪代码示意\nif (oldDeps === null) {\n  // 首次渲染，一定执行\n  return true;\n}\nfor (let i = 0; i &lt; oldDeps.length; i++) {\n  if (!Object.is(newDeps[i], oldDeps[i])) {\n    return true; // 有变化，需要执行\n  }\n}\nreturn false; // 无变化，跳过</code></pre><p id=\"ub8f0e0f5\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">注意：依赖数组的</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">长度必须保持不变</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，否则 React 会抛出警告（因为长度变化意味着调用顺序可能被破坏）。</span></p><hr id=\"izC6P\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"N2WUy\"><span class=\"ne-text\">4. 特殊情况的处理</span></h2><h3 id=\"OM8Fr\"><span class=\"ne-text\">4.1 空依赖数组 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">[]</span></code></h3><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u475ada11\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">首次渲染时会记录依赖数组 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">[]</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">。</span></li><li id=\"u014970c0\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">后续更新时，由于依赖项个数为 0，比较结果永远为“无变化”，因此 Effect 只执行一次（类似 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">componentDidMount</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">），清理函数在组件卸载时执行（类似 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">componentWillUnmount</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">）。</span></li></ul><h3 id=\"hXvGx\"><span class=\"ne-text\">4.2 不传第二个参数</span></h3><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u6f39d7a9\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">相当于没有依赖数组，React 会在每次渲染后都执行 Effect（先清理再执行），不进行任何跳过判断。</span></li></ul><h3 id=\"vgN4W\"><span class=\"ne-text\">4.3 依赖项为引用类型</span></h3><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u7d30b203\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果依赖项是对象、数组或函数，React 比较的是它们的</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">引用地址</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，而不是内容。例如：</span></li></ul><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"KVEXG\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>const [user, setUser] = useState({ name: 'Alice' });\nuseEffect(() =&gt; {}, [user]); // 即使 user 内容不变，但若 setUser({ name: 'Alice' }) 传入新对象，引用变化，Effect 会执行。</code></pre><p id=\"ue26b650e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">为避免不必要的执行，通常需要稳定依赖（如使用 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useMemo</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">/</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useCallback</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 或基于值的比较）。</span></p><hr id=\"iH7Rh\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"XLzd0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">5. 为什么必须保证调用顺序不变？</span></h2><p id=\"uf6061061\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">因为 React 完全依赖</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">调用顺序</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">来匹配每个 Hook 的依赖数组。如果 Hooks 被放在条件语句中，渲染顺序可能变化，导致链表索引错乱，React 会把前一个 Hook 的依赖数组误认为是后一个 Hook 的，从而引发 bug。这也是 Hooks 规则中强调“只在最顶层调用 Hooks”的根本原因。</span></p><hr id=\"ZLwpf\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"FFMZV\"><span class=\"ne-text\">6. 总结</span></h2><p id=\"u31b2bb8c\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Hooks 依赖数组的原理可以归结为：</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">React 在 Fiber 节点上按调用顺序存储每个 Hook 的上一次依赖数组，更新时使用 </span></strong><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code><strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 逐个比较新旧依赖项，从而决定是否跳过本次更新。</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 这一机制既保证了性能，又要求开发者遵循 Hooks 的调用规则。</span></p></div>","body_draft_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"paragraphSpacing\" content=\"relax\" /><p data-lake-id=\"u1944b30a\" id=\"u1944b30a\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufaab4825\" id=\"ufaab4825\">Hooks 的依赖数组是 React 用来判断 Effect、Memo 或 Callback 是否需要重新执行的核心机制。其原理可以概括为：</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua63e6f7a\" id=\"ua63e6f7a\">基于调用顺序和浅比较，决定是否跳过更新</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u436d06ba\" id=\"u436d06ba\">。下面从设计目的、底层存储、比较逻辑以及注意事项四个方面详细说明。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22W4bWp%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"DDsnA\" id=\"DDsnA\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5249c0ce\" id=\"u5249c0ce\">1. 依赖数组的设计目的</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"uc86e36ef\" id=\"uc86e36ef\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0bfbed4c\" id=\"u0bfbed4c\">依赖数组让开发者能够声明式地指定 Hooks 所依赖的外部值（如 props、state）。当组件重新渲染时，React 会比较依赖项的新旧值：</span></p><ul list=\"u1edc8ef2\"><li fid=\"u556711a6\" data-lake-id=\"ufcd6e49b\" id=\"ufcd6e49b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6053b1e4\" id=\"u6053b1e4\">如果所有依赖项都未变化，则跳过本次 Effect 的执行（或返回缓存的 Memo/Callback 值）。</span></li><li fid=\"u556711a6\" data-lake-id=\"u1bab1189\" id=\"u1bab1189\"><span data-lake-id=\"u51f08543\" id=\"u51f08543\">如果有任何依赖项发生变化，则执行 Effect（或重新计算 Memo/Callback）。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"ue3248bd5\" id=\"ue3248bd5\"><span data-lake-id=\"ucf880c98\" id=\"ucf880c98\">这避免了不必要的计算和副作用，是 React 性能优化的重要手段。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22YymDj%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"I4f21\" id=\"I4f21\"><span data-lake-id=\"ueea03945\" id=\"ueea03945\">2. 底层存储：Fiber 中的 Hooks 链表</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"uf6a8a86f\" id=\"uf6a8a86f\"><span data-lake-id=\"uaad4c04f\" id=\"uaad4c04f\">每个函数组件对应一个 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ucd5f272f\" id=\"ucd5f272f\">Fiber 节点</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5032d4af\" id=\"u5032d4af\">，该节点上的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u9a5eabef\" id=\"u9a5eabef\"><span data-lake-id=\"uee3402b0\" id=\"uee3402b0\">memoizedState</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u82640cde\" id=\"u82640cde\"> 属性指向一个</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue2ccd91a\" id=\"ue2ccd91a\">链表</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc60a3d35\" id=\"uc60a3d35\">，链表中的每个节点对应组件中使用的一个 Hook（如 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ue23f227f\" id=\"ue23f227f\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub7c1b786\" id=\"ub7c1b786\">useState</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u36c29938\" id=\"u36c29938\">、</span><code data-lake-id=\"u09e2fa49\" id=\"u09e2fa49\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6a6f88df\" id=\"u6a6f88df\">useEffect</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u49845f6c\" id=\"u49845f6c\">、</span><code data-lake-id=\"u3238fe44\" id=\"u3238fe44\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2fa56089\" id=\"u2fa56089\">useCallback</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ua8dfdf31\" id=\"ua8dfdf31\"> 等）。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ua238f010\" id=\"ua238f010\"><span data-lake-id=\"u81c5f88c\" id=\"u81c5f88c\">对于 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ubfb03ea4\" id=\"ubfb03ea4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u38d5e6bb\" id=\"u38d5e6bb\">useEffect</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uf1653209\" id=\"uf1653209\">，其 Hook 节点内部会存储：</span></p><ul list=\"uf4cc3484\"><li fid=\"ue48b4381\" data-lake-id=\"ufbe61cae\" id=\"ufbe61cae\"><code data-lake-id=\"ua06d4d07\" id=\"ua06d4d07\"><span data-lake-id=\"uab65ff65\" id=\"uab65ff65\">create</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u05965911\" id=\"u05965911\">：effect 函数。</span></li><li fid=\"ue48b4381\" data-lake-id=\"u89bd33b1\" id=\"u89bd33b1\"><code data-lake-id=\"ub90a5449\" id=\"ub90a5449\"><span data-lake-id=\"uabdcb845\" id=\"uabdcb845\">destroy</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ufbf98311\" id=\"ufbf98311\">：上一次执行返回的清理函数。</span></li><li fid=\"ue48b4381\" data-lake-id=\"ua845a2c2\" id=\"ua845a2c2\"><code data-lake-id=\"u3a95f0e8\" id=\"u3a95f0e8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u102f4f4f\" id=\"u102f4f4f\">deps</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ud18e24cc\" id=\"ud18e24cc\">：上一次渲染时传入的依赖数组。</span></li><li fid=\"ue48b4381\" data-lake-id=\"u88be6786\" id=\"u88be6786\"><code data-lake-id=\"u43d93679\" id=\"u43d93679\"><span data-lake-id=\"u58a93fda\" id=\"u58a93fda\">next</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u94707b9f\" id=\"u94707b9f\">：指向下一个 Hook 的指针。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"uf3eacb3b\" id=\"uf3eacb3b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8c117bc7\" id=\"u8c117bc7\">当组件更新时，React 会按</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uec04c290\" id=\"uec04c290\">绝对相同的顺序</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u98b43201\" id=\"u98b43201\">遍历这个链表，依次取出每个 Hook 的上一次依赖数组，与本次传入的新依赖数组进行比较。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22CR80o%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"BmtMh\" id=\"BmtMh\"><span data-lake-id=\"u73e1b1f2\" id=\"u73e1b1f2\">3. 比较逻辑：浅比较（</span><code data-lake-id=\"ua1a5d29c\" id=\"ua1a5d29c\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7a2de18a\" id=\"u7a2de18a\">Object.is</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u4fa15a88\" id=\"u4fa15a88\">）</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u9f9282b4\" id=\"u9f9282b4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u94077698\" id=\"u94077698\">React 使用 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u9f42b93b\" id=\"u9f42b93b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4fa5b147\" id=\"u4fa5b147\">Object.is</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ud58e6804\" id=\"ud58e6804\"> 对依赖项进行逐个比较，其行为与 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u4a5cc75d\" id=\"u4a5cc75d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u069c2360\" id=\"u069c2360\">===</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"udc94a092\" id=\"udc94a092\"> 基本一致，但有两个特例：</span></p><ul list=\"u212b77b1\"><li fid=\"ua5d878cf\" data-lake-id=\"u49718422\" id=\"u49718422\"><code data-lake-id=\"uec53e75b\" id=\"uec53e75b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4bab5282\" id=\"u4bab5282\">NaN === NaN</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u4ce85a61\" id=\"u4ce85a61\"> 为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u36370738\" id=\"u36370738\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9ed98771\" id=\"u9ed98771\">false</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u05ce7183\" id=\"u05ce7183\">，而 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u26e658ba\" id=\"u26e658ba\"><span data-lake-id=\"u97e29458\" id=\"u97e29458\">Object.is(NaN, NaN)</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ua1521cda\" id=\"ua1521cda\"> 为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u49089610\" id=\"u49089610\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6c485cce\" id=\"u6c485cce\">true</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ub1414e2b\" id=\"ub1414e2b\">。</span></li><li fid=\"ua5d878cf\" data-lake-id=\"ufced60f1\" id=\"ufced60f1\"><code data-lake-id=\"u4e175f7e\" id=\"u4e175f7e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u04334cb7\" id=\"u04334cb7\">+0 === -0</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uf22ec731\" id=\"uf22ec731\"> 为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ufdaa8919\" id=\"ufdaa8919\"><span data-lake-id=\"ueec2e000\" id=\"ueec2e000\">true</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u9af737fc\" id=\"u9af737fc\">，而 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ua8c3bc98\" id=\"ua8c3bc98\"><span data-lake-id=\"uead8f67c\" id=\"uead8f67c\">Object.is(+0, -0)</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u6ec08727\" id=\"u6ec08727\"> 为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uc9990e4d\" id=\"uc9990e4d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u82445473\" id=\"u82445473\">false</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u4e3c0d10\" id=\"u4e3c0d10\">。</span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id=\"BVDEZ\" id=\"BVDEZ\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua07e1107\" id=\"ua07e1107\">比较过程</span></h3><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%2F%2F%20%E4%BC%AA%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E7%A4%BA%E6%84%8F%5Cnif%20(oldDeps%20%3D%3D%3D%20null)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%2F%2F%20%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E6%B8%B2%E6%9F%93%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%5Cn%20%20return%20true%3B%5Cn%7D%5Cnfor%20(let%20i%20%3D%200%3B%20i%20%3C%20oldDeps.length%3B%20i%2B%2B)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20if%20(!Object.is(newDeps%5Bi%5D%2C%20oldDeps%5Bi%5D))%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20true%3B%20%2F%2F%20%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%8C%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%5Cn%20%20%7D%5Cn%7D%5Cnreturn%20false%3B%20%2F%2F%20%E6%97%A0%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%8C%E8%B7%B3%E8%BF%87%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22mbDns%22%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"ub8f0e0f5\" id=\"ub8f0e0f5\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5b260b57\" id=\"u5b260b57\">注意：依赖数组的</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua532ddaa\" id=\"ua532ddaa\">长度必须保持不变</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5aa17101\" id=\"u5aa17101\">，否则 React 会抛出警告（因为长度变化意味着调用顺序可能被破坏）。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22izC6P%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"N2WUy\" id=\"N2WUy\"><span data-lake-id=\"u81c2c8c9\" id=\"u81c2c8c9\">4. 特殊情况的处理</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id=\"OM8Fr\" id=\"OM8Fr\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4bdff763\" id=\"u4bdff763\">4.1 空依赖数组 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u0d2a2372\" id=\"u0d2a2372\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8df72e76\" id=\"u8df72e76\">[]</span></code></h3><ul list=\"u0b89e119\"><li fid=\"u44f1140a\" data-lake-id=\"u475ada11\" id=\"u475ada11\"><span data-lake-id=\"u70c5f60a\" id=\"u70c5f60a\">首次渲染时会记录依赖数组 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u52a246d6\" id=\"u52a246d6\"><span data-lake-id=\"u86b788a3\" id=\"u86b788a3\">[]</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ub8d58b0b\" id=\"ub8d58b0b\">。</span></li><li fid=\"u44f1140a\" data-lake-id=\"u014970c0\" id=\"u014970c0\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3f031eea\" id=\"u3f031eea\">后续更新时，由于依赖项个数为 0，比较结果永远为“无变化”，因此 Effect 只执行一次（类似 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u60f73b39\" id=\"u60f73b39\"><span data-lake-id=\"u15144966\" id=\"u15144966\">componentDidMount</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uff798836\" id=\"uff798836\">），清理函数在组件卸载时执行（类似 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u142eedfc\" id=\"u142eedfc\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue3aec64b\" id=\"ue3aec64b\">componentWillUnmount</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u788e10fb\" id=\"u788e10fb\">）。</span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id=\"hXvGx\" id=\"hXvGx\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1761fb70\" id=\"u1761fb70\">4.2 不传第二个参数</span></h3><ul list=\"ufb82370b\"><li fid=\"ue07d3b77\" data-lake-id=\"u6f39d7a9\" id=\"u6f39d7a9\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf9a7d0ef\" id=\"uf9a7d0ef\">相当于没有依赖数组，React 会在每次渲染后都执行 Effect（先清理再执行），不进行任何跳过判断。</span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id=\"vgN4W\" id=\"vgN4W\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5b3ac037\" id=\"u5b3ac037\">4.3 依赖项为引用类型</span></h3><ul list=\"uaaaa7a89\"><li fid=\"u17ce8fc9\" data-lake-id=\"u7d30b203\" id=\"u7d30b203\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3c202496\" id=\"u3c202496\">如果依赖项是对象、数组或函数，React 比较的是它们的</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u493fa7e2\" id=\"u493fa7e2\">引用地址</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua23fdab2\" id=\"ua23fdab2\">，而不是内容。例如：</span></li></ul><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22const%20%5Buser%2C%20setUser%5D%20%3D%20useState(%7B%20name%3A%20'Alice'%20%7D)%3B%5CnuseEffect(()%20%3D%3E%20%7B%7D%2C%20%5Buser%5D)%3B%20%2F%2F%20%E5%8D%B3%E4%BD%BF%20user%20%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%98%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E8%8B%A5%20setUser(%7B%20name%3A%20'Alice'%20%7D)%20%E4%BC%A0%E5%85%A5%E6%96%B0%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%95%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%8CEffect%20%E4%BC%9A%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%82%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22KVEXG%22%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"ue26b650e\" id=\"ue26b650e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u15f34c80\" id=\"u15f34c80\">为避免不必要的执行，通常需要稳定依赖（如使用 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u7bc11d22\" id=\"u7bc11d22\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8d112582\" id=\"u8d112582\">useMemo</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u82729571\" id=\"u82729571\">/</span><code data-lake-id=\"u291db80b\" id=\"u291db80b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u88e3bb11\" id=\"u88e3bb11\">useCallback</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u951d4020\" id=\"u951d4020\"> 或基于值的比较）。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22iH7Rh%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"XLzd0\" id=\"XLzd0\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud7c1f25c\" id=\"ud7c1f25c\">5. 为什么必须保证调用顺序不变？</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"uf6061061\" id=\"uf6061061\"><span data-lake-id=\"u955a842f\" id=\"u955a842f\">因为 React 完全依赖</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2f2416e3\" id=\"u2f2416e3\">调用顺序</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5c4dec04\" id=\"u5c4dec04\">来匹配每个 Hook 的依赖数组。如果 Hooks 被放在条件语句中，渲染顺序可能变化，导致链表索引错乱，React 会把前一个 Hook 的依赖数组误认为是后一个 Hook 的，从而引发 bug。这也是 Hooks 规则中强调“只在最顶层调用 Hooks”的根本原因。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22ZLwpf%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"FFMZV\" id=\"FFMZV\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3d67ff26\" id=\"u3d67ff26\">6. 总结</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u31b2bb8c\" id=\"u31b2bb8c\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2e6250bd\" id=\"u2e6250bd\">Hooks 依赖数组的原理可以归结为：</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5ee4d6d4\" id=\"u5ee4d6d4\">React 在 Fiber 节点上按调用顺序存储每个 Hook 的上一次依赖数组，更新时使用 </span></strong><code data-lake-id=\"u8d5ac40d\" id=\"u8d5ac40d\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf979c216\" id=\"uf979c216\">Object.is</span></code><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5c2948c7\" id=\"u5c2948c7\"> 逐个比较新旧依赖项，从而决定是否跳过本次更新。</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uddcb8fd2\" id=\"uddcb8fd2\"> 这一机制既保证了性能，又要求开发者遵循 Hooks 的调用规则。</span></p>","word_count":1086,"slug":"odg7qxrltb1iy3un","type":"Doc","title":"说说 Hooks 的依赖数组原理","public":1,"cover":null,"custom_cover":null,"description":"Hooks 的依赖数组是 React 用来判断 Effect、Memo 或 Callback 是否需要重新执行的核心机制。其原理可以概括为：基于调用顺序和浅比较，决定是否跳过更新。下面从设计目的、底层存储、比较逻辑以及注意事项四个方面详细说明。1. 依赖数组的设计目的依赖数组让开发者能够声明式...","custom_description":"","format":"lake","status":1,"read_status":1,"editor_meta":"{\"hr\":6,\"codeblock\":2}","user_id":200222,"created_at":"2026-03-04T09:37:00.000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-06T08:24:07.000Z","published_at":"2026-03-04T09:37:22.000Z","first_published_at":"2026-03-04T09:37:22.211Z","content_updated_at":"2026-03-04T09:37:22.000Z","id":259479562},"doc_digest":"oNL0rP1Z9WYhRZaSYYNuXTty1nA"}